>>> easily/efficiently be loaded.
>>>=20
>>> Just did a test and a on-disk index of 8658 blocks (via "du -s" ) turne=
d
>>> into
>>> a zip file of 4275 blocks, thus approx 50% compression is possible.
>>>=20
