>C:\lucene-1.2>java org.apache.lucene.demo.IndexFiles  <path>
>Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NoClassDefFoundError: org/apache/lucene/dem
>o/IndexFiles
>
>I even tried with -cp "lucene-1.2-rc4.jar;lucene-demos-1_2-rc4.jar" ...
>to no avail.
