>//
>//	===========================================================================
>//
>//	Title:		SZIndex.java
>//	Description:	[Description]
>//	Author:		Raphael Szwarc <raphael_szwarc@hotmail.com>
>//	Creation Date:	Wed Sep 12 2001
>//	Legal:		Copyright (C) 2001 Raphael Szwarc. All Rights Reserved.
